### Steps to reproduce

This PR is the continuation of https://github.com/flutter/flutter/issues/137423.
The idea is to simplify the sample and provide more precise data for you guys to test.

Lottie performs great on Impeller iOS but on android the performance is slow and laggy (pretty evident on middle and entry level phones).We think this might be due to a perf. issue that Impeller android has with images when multiple images are on the scene (this is something that occurs even with still images). Fixing this issue may prolly improve images rendering at large on android. 

### Expected results

Better performance. No janks.

### Actual results

Slow performance. Janks.

